I '''Steven Allan Spielberg''' (mibait Diciembre 18, 1946)<ref>{{cite book| last = McBride| first = Joseph| title = Steven Spielberg| publisher = Faber and Faber|year=1997| isbn = 0-571-19177-0|page=37}}</ref> metung yang [[Estados Unidos|Americanu]]ng direktor pelikula, talasulat senaryo, prodyuser, ampong maragul a negosyanti. King kayang karerang maygit apat a dekada, dakal na la asaklong tema ampong uri ning pelikula deng kayang obra. Deng minuna nang pelikulang science-fiction ampong adventure tuturing dong menimuna kareng modernung Hollywood blockbuster. Kareng mas tauling banwa, linub ya kareng isyung anti king [[Holocaust]], ing kalakal kareng lipat ning Atlanticu (''transatlantic slave trade''), [[gera]], ampong [[terorismu]]. TUturing deng metung kareng pekasikat ampong pekamaimpluwensyang gagawang pelikula king amlat ning pelikula.<ref>''The cinema of Steven Spielberg: Empire of light''. Nigel Morris. Wallflower Press. 2007</ref> Metung ya murin kareng mitátag king [[DreamWorks]] movie studio.

Simbut neng Spielberg ing [[Academy Award for Best Director]] para king ''[[Schindler's List]]'' (1993) ampong ''[[Saving Private Ryan]]'' (1998). Deng atlu kareng pelikula nang Spielberg films—''[[Jaws (film)|Jaws]]'' (1975), ''[[E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial]]'' (1982), ampong ''[[Jurassic Park (film)|Jurassic Park]]'' (1993)—menikwa lang [[List of highest-grossing films|box office]] record, at balang metung meging pekaragaul penakitan anyang panaun a ita. Ngeni, ing e milikas o mekumberting pangkabilugan a penakitan da reng anggang pelikulang dinirek nang Spielberg, maygit king $8.5&nbsp;bilyun king mabilug a yatu. Tatantyan ne ning [[Forbes]] ing alaga ning bandi nang Spielberg a $3.2&nbsp;bilyun.<ref name="forbes1"/>

